  "body": "https://github.com/miekg/dns/commit/d051b464e9f024b65ce9674dece9d3e905b31828 adds dns.Truncate which linearly goes of the message and truncates. This is more efficient than the current binary search implementation we have.\r\n\r\ncoredns: binary search log2(n) Len's on the _entire message_\r\ndns: Len(n) on the entire message.\r\n\r\nThe gist being: we are `Len`-ing mutiple times over the same RR currently, while the dns impl. just `Len`s once over each RRs. ",
